8 An Act relating to retirement; amending 47 O.S. 2021,
Section 2-300, as last amended by Section 1, Chapter
9 45, O.S.L. 2025 (47 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 2-300),
which relates to the Oklahoma Law Enforcement
10 Retirement System; defining term; providing for
participation of certain new employees in the
11 Oklahoma Law Enforcement Retirement System; providing
for codification; and declaring an emergency.
12
13
